{"tid":638501,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]有冇人試過突然咁？。。。","createTime":"2018-04-22T18:27:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T04:12:54.000Z","uid":29485,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f6bbfdd112ac6b96561b4e85e1200bd70b097ef8","tid":638501,"uid":29485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T18:27:21.000Z","msg":"頭先我一路瞓係張床到禁緊電話 睇facebook<br />\n突然feel到隻手濕咗 本身隻手掂住張被 以為張被濕 心諗唔係今朝個q仲未乾啊？<br />\n望一望隻手 係我隻手濕左<br />\n我隻手係有滴水係到流緊<br />\n望返岩岩掂到張被個位又冇濕 好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟啲水係邊到黎 <br />\n<br />\n你地有冇試過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有少少驚<br />\n<br />\n其實之前都有試過夜晚屋企人瞓哂 我係廁所屙緊屎<br />\n又係molala有滴水滴落我大脾 不過廁所有水唔奇 雖然我望均哂成個廁所都係乾 但個地方係廁所 都有得解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc20cc7d89f19d8d9967d13812a58eb129fe43fd","tid":638501,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T18:28:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"15312795ebda3b9a815936933872e4ea83efcdb4","tid":638501,"uid":54785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T18:32:35.000Z","msg":"試過, 有排成日係D 騎呢位有水滴中我, 留意左好多次係無可能有水<br />\n<br />\n係屋企中果陣亦都摸過天花係乾"},{"pid":"3ff1f7e052355ec487954ea00f0b21008c48937d","tid":638501,"uid":5190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T18:33:32.000Z","msg":"樓上條屍出水啫 唔使驚"},{"pid":"3d3c602ccf86ec51a5f6337b5c80ace346d769f7","tid":638501,"uid":29485,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T18:34:03.000Z","msg":"補圖 係咁樣流<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dccc881521e536ed7d1cb9d847f7014fc96d3578","tid":638501,"uid":136896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-